%description monitoring
Tools developed for monitoring OpenShift.

%files monitoring
%dir %{python_sitelib}/openshift_tools/monitoring
%{python_sitelib}/openshift_tools/monitoring/*.py
%{python_sitelib}/openshift_tools/monitoring/*.py[co]


